          "process_md": "> **Registration**\n\n\n1. Applicant need to follow the [official website](https://www.jk.gov.in/jkeservices/home).1. Click on the [registration ](https://www.jk.gov.in/jkeservices/cznregistration)button and provide the following details.\n  - Citizen Registration Details.\n  - Last Resided/Current Address Details.\n  - Permanent Address Details.\n  - Additional Details.\n  - Login Details.\n\n1. Submit\n\n<br>\n\n> **Login &amp; Apply**\n\n\n1. Login on the [official website](https://www.jk.gov.in/jkeservices/home).1. Click on e-services and select **Finance/Mission youth** _option._1. Fill out the application form and vehicle details. \n1. Upload the required documents.\n\n  - Driver Photograph.\n  - Domicile Certificate/Ration Card.\n  - Birth Certificate.\n  - Applicant Driving License.\n  - Driver Driving License.\n  - Affidavit.\n  - Unemployment Certificate. \n\n1. Submit.\n\n"
        }
